---
layout: layouts/app.njk
title: Freewriting
dek: Timed sessions to reduce inhibition and keep the pen moving.
---

<div class="ss-stack">
  <section class="ss-panel ss-stack">
    <header class="ss-stack" style="gap: var(--ss-space-2)">
      <h2 style="margin: 0">Freewrite</h2>
      <p class="ss-muted" style="margin: 0">Plain text on purpose. Formatting is stripped when you paste, so you can keep moving.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="ss-submitteditor ss-stack" data-ss-submission-editor data-ss-mode="freewrite" data-word-limit="2000">
      <div class="ss-submitteditor__row">
        <span class="ss-submitteditor__meta ss-muted" aria-live="polite">
          <span data-ss-wordcount>0</span> words
        </span>
      </div>

      <div class="ss-submitteditor__help ss-muted">
        Tip: set a timer on your phone (5–15 minutes) and don’t edit. This won’t save yet.
      </div>

      <div class="ss-submitteditor__editorwrap">
        <div
          class="ss-submitteditor__editor ss-submission"
          contenteditable="true"
          spellcheck="true"
          role="textbox"
          aria-multiline="true"
          data-ss-editor
        ><p class="ss-noindent">Start writing…</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
